comment: Horford (BOS) is in the paint area actively guarding an opponent.
Thomas (BOS) makes marginal contact with DeRozan (TOR) that does not affect his SQBR.
Valanciunas (TOR) maintains legal guarding position on the drive to the basket by Thomas (BOS).
RHH shows Thomas (BOS) moves his pivot foot on the gather.
Valanciunas (TOR) cleanly blocks the shot attempt by Thomas (BOS).
Crowder (BOS) makes incidental contact with DeRozan (TOR) that does not affect his SQBR.
Valanciunas (TOR) blocks the shot attempt by Green (BOS) and makes incidental "high-five" contact.
Thomas (BOS) makes marginal contact with Lowry (TOR) that does not affect his SQBR.
Horford (BOS) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Lowry (TOR) on his driving shot attempt.
Valanciunas (TOR) makes contact with the ball after it is outside of the cylinder.
Lowry (TOR) makes contact with the ball on the inbound, reestablishes himself inbounds, and retrieves the loose ball.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court (jump ball) was overturned. BOS ball.
Lowry (TOR) makes incidental contact with Smart (BOS) that does not affect his pass attempt.
Carroll (TOR) and Crowder (BOS) make incidental contact with one another while attempting to retrieve the loose ball.
The ball is last touched by Carroll (TOR) prior to going OOB.
Thomas (BOS) makes marginal contact with Joseph (TOR) prior to receiving the inbound pass.
Valanciunas (TOR) makes contact with Thomas' (BOS) arms that affects his driving shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) commits a take foul on Joseph (TOR).
